e spare time I like to sit down and type away about our day I write the good and the bad. So i thought why not air were not the only family if we can offer support and receive it back it's just a bonus. #autismawareness #autistic #beautifuljourney  the only way I see autism is taking the more scenic route in life and my God il be their to hold her hand and share every single view she endures. üíôüíôüíôüíôüíôüíôüíô";}i:121;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:1;}i:122;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:1;}i:123;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEvSKiWnbap";}i:124;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:238:"https://scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/118885888_981750768957371_1960171213979741719_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=111&_nc_ohc=AWBtzWX9qqgAX9QfTz9&oh=ba7adc3a3c42f74988d967f2e1f27a08&oe=5F7CC269";}i:125;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:5:"image";}i:126;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:23523728112;}i:127;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:128;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:129;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:130;a:1:{s:2:"id";s:19:"2391209354500792770";}i:131;a:1:{s:10:"short_code";s:11:"CEvSD0enGHC";}i:132;a:1:{s:12:"created_time";i:1599274390;}i:133;a:1:{s:7:"caption";s:163:"SO many cool items with artwork by my son Joey are for sale on his website - JosephPetersArt.com please check it out and support an artist with autism üß©üíïüôè";}i:134;a:1:{s:14:"comments_count";i:1;}i:135;a:1:{s:11:"likes_count";i:3;}i:136;a:1:{s:4:"link";s:39:"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEvSD0enGHC";}i:137;a:1:{s:5:"image";s:249:"https://scontent-sin6-2.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.2885-15/e35/s1080x1080/118794548_303933894235222_7280694658917278671_n.jpg?_nc_ht=scontent-sin6-2.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=110&_nc_ohc=mFAKgXAqdfMAX-5VEE7&oh=57028e90b50a65b2131ba80bc495722b&oe=5F7D2BF9";}i:138;a:1:{s:4:"type";s:7:"sidecar";}i:139;a:1:{s:8:"owner_id";i:10507824;}i:140;a:1:{s:14:"owner_username";s:0:"";}i:141;a:1:{s:14:"owner_fullname";s:0:"";}i:142;a:1:{s:9:"owner_pic";s:0:"";}i:143;a:1